      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it runs well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some clear coat fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains comfortable. It has been maintained regularly, but potential buyers should expect the typical mechanical wear associated with its mileage. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
