    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable ride that's easy on the wallet? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it still runs well and offers a comfortable, functional interior. It\u2019s a great choice for anyone looking for a dependable car with plenty of life left at a fantastic price!",
