      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare find for the discerning buyer. It looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered new, with flawless exterior paint and a pristine interior that shows no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment. You can expect a showroom-quality vehicle that requires nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
